name: ImmigrationStatus
title: Immigration Status
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values addresses terms representing an observation of immigration status or citizenship.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have a/an assessment of the person's status with immigrating to their current country of residence.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes LOINC codes for Immigration Status.),(Exclusion Criteria: Terms not representative of observable encoded terms that may have values indicating Immigration Status.)
